License of the fetched data
===========================

This repository does NOT distribute the GeoJSON files in this directory.
Operators fetch them at first-time setup directly from OpenStreetMap Japan
(see README.md for the procedure).

When an operator fetches them, the resulting files are licensed under BOTH
of the following, simultaneously:

  * Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 2.0 Generic (CC-BY-SA 2.0)
    https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/

  * Open Database License (ODbL) 1.0
    https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/1-0/

Source:
  Polygon coordinates extracted from OpenStreetMap Japan vector tilesets
  `hoppo` and `takeshima`, served at https://tile.openstreetmap.jp/.

  Per OSMFJ's site-wide license declaration
  (https://www.openstreetmap.jp/terms_and_privacy):
    - Tile data: CC-BY-SA 2.0
    - Underlying OSM geographic data: ODbL 1.0
                                      (© OpenStreetMap contributors)

Required attribution if the operator redistributes the fetched files:

    © OpenStreetMap contributors (ODbL).
    Disputed-island polygons derived from OpenStreetMap Japan
    (https://tile.openstreetmap.jp/, CC-BY-SA 2.0).

Scope:
  This LICENSE describes the license that applies to the fetched data IF
  AND WHEN it is fetched per README.md. The repository itself remains
  uniformly under GPL-2.0 (see the top-level LICENSE).

  The CC-BY-SA 2.0 / ODbL share-alike obligation does NOT propagate into
  the deployed MBTiles produced from these files; see README.md and
  tileserver-noborder.md §13 for details.
